Package: SpikeTrainPatternDetector
Type: Package
Title: Spike Train Pattern Detector
Version: 1.2.1
Authors@R: person(given = "Houchun", family = "Zhou", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "zhouhouchun@outlook.com")
Author: Houchun Zhou [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Houchun Zhou <zhouhouchun@outlook.com>
Description: Productized Shiny-based spike train pattern detector and semi-supervised review platform. The package provides quality control, rule-based candidate detection, eventness audit, Mean-ISI and Pasquale logISIH/newBD threshold support layers, train-wise threshold suggestions, and reproducible export reports without treating support-layer results as final ground truth.
